A determinancy diagram, sometimes known as a [[dependency diagram]], is a diagram which documents the [[determinancy]] or dependency between a set of data items.<ref>Beynon-Davies P. (2004). Database Systems 3rd Edition. Palgrave, Basingstoke, UK. {{ISBN|1-4039-1601-2}}</ref> Determinancy diagrams are particularly used as an aid to [[database normalization]].

